OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777978995
OL,3,CDozens dead after firework factory
OL,4,Cexplosion in China
OL,6,FAn explosion at a fireworks factory in
OL,7,FChina has killed at least 26 people
OL,8,Fand injured 61 others, according to
OL,9,Fauthorities.
OL,11,FNearly 500 rescue workers and three
OL,12,Frobots were deployed to the scene in
OL,13,Fthe city of Liuyang, in the central
OL,14,Fprovince of Hunan, on Monday
OL,15,Fafternoon, China's official news
OL,16,Fagency Xinhua said.
OL,18,FNearby residents were also evacuated
OL,19,Fover fears of further explosions from
OL,20,Ftwo nearby black powder warehouses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
