PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777978995
OL,3,CDozens dead after firework factory
OL,4,Cexplosion in China
OL,6,FAerial footage from state broadcaster
OL,7,FCCTV showed white smoke still
OL,8,Fbillowing from parts of the site and
OL,9,Fcollapsed or damaged buildings.
OL,11,FAuthorities were investigating the
OL,12,Fcause of the blast and police have
OL,13,Fdetained the person in charge of the
OL,14,Fcompany, Xinhua said.
OL,16,FChinese President Xi Jinping called
OL,17,Ffor "all-out efforts" to search for
OL,18,Fpeople who are still unaccounted for
OL,19,Fand for authorities to investigate the
OL,20,Fcause swiftly and pursue serious
OL,21,Faccountability, the report said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
