OL,3,CDozens dead after firework factory
OL,4,Cexplosion in China
OL,6,FThe city of Liuyang has a long history
OL,7,Fof fireworks production.
OL,9,FThe Guinness World Records said the
OL,10,Ffirst accurately documented firework,
OL,11,Fthe Chinese firecracker, was
OL,12,Fattributed to Li Tian, a monk who
OL,13,Flived near Liuyang during China's Tang
OL,14,Fdynasty, dating to around 618 to 907
OL,15,FC.E.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
